# Exercise 16: View Machine Information

### Display System Information

```bash
hostnamectl
```

### Observe

Identify:

* Hostname
* Operating System
* Kernel Version
* Architecture
* Machine ID
* Boot ID

---

# Exercise 17: Change Hostname

### Set New Hostname

```bash
hostnamectl set-hostname server1.example.com
```

### Verify

```bash
hostnamectl
```

```bash
hostname
```

### Expected Result

New hostname should be displayed.

